I"q<p>By practicing self compassion we can provide ourselves with the need for reassurance and a sense of safety in the absence of another person.</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Notice the critical inner narrative</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Notice the tension in your body created by these critical thoughts and beliefs</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Bring awareness to the areas of tension without resisting them</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Breathe softly to these areas of tension to help release the built up stress and tension</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Replace critical thoughts with supportive and reassuring statements</p>
  </li>
</ol>
